WEBVTT

00:00.050 --> 00:01.550
_

00:01.576 --> 00:02.839
We slept together.

00:02.865 --> 00:04.445
She said you raped her.

00:04.471 --> 00:06.336
- I love you, Katy.
- Stop it.

00:06.362 --> 00:08.242
Andrew Earlham's wife took an overdose.

00:08.268 --> 00:10.753
No evidence it was anything
other than suicide.

00:10.779 --> 00:13.319
The CPS won't be prosecuting your case.

00:13.345 --> 00:15.109
You don't want to come in
for a drink, do you?

00:15.200 --> 00:17.395
I don't drink with men who rape women.

00:17.421 --> 00:18.840
I broke into Andrew's house.

00:18.880 --> 00:20.080
Please help me.

00:20.120 --> 00:21.476
- What's going on?
- Andrew Earlham,

00:21.502 --> 00:23.067
we have a warrant to search your house.

00:23.093 --> 00:26.733
Lawsuits for defamation of character
can be a lengthy process.

00:26.759 --> 00:27.959
Oh, I know.

00:28.144 --> 00:31.000
Building my life to what it is today
was a lengthy process

00:31.040 --> 00:32.478
but she took a wrecking ball to that.

00:32.503 --> 00:33.745
She owes me.

